metadata.name: All our Gods are Dead
metadata.description:
"All our Gods are Dead" by BryantW

He just stood there and smiled with all his crooked rotten teeth as all our Gods Died in our dreams.

This artwork was created using public domain images collage together and remixed with patterns and other effects in Photoshop.

5120px x 5120px .jpg - Date of completion 7/4/2022

About the artist - Bryant W. is a broken child born of the 80â€™s using his artistic skills to help the world find beauty within the ugliness that surrounds us all.
